t.</p></physDesc></msDesc></witness></listWit></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><langUsage><language ident="de-AT">German</language></langUsage><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><persName ref="#pmb12438">Adam, Robert</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">Wien</placeName><date when="1917-11-23" n="01">23. 11. 1917</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">Wien</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><tei:ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb12438">Adam, Robert</tei:ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1917-11-05_01">Adam an Schnitzler, 5. 11. 1917</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1918-06-11_01">Schnitzler an Adam, 11. 6. 1918</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
